WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
I am Tsurukichi Maruyama, the chairman of the Central Committee for the Conquering of the Election.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:14.000
I hope that in the next election of the vice-chairmen of the parliament and the general assembly,

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:25.000
all the members of the country will be able to vote in a correct and good way, unlike in the past.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
The elections have been very expensive, so the parliament must have been worried about money since the day of the election.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Rather than working for the politics on behalf of the members,

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
many people are willing to make a living by making money.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:49.000
This is the basis for making the shape of the parliament worse.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:56.000
The government uses money for nothing, so it makes unreasonable decisions.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:02.000
Fortunately, even if the election is won and the cabinet is formed,

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:07.000
the unreasonable decisions appear on the political agenda.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:17.000
In other words, there are all the causes of the hellish incidents in the parliament and the cabinet being evacuated.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:29.000
When young people see this and know the love of politics with such a dark shadow,

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:37.000
they will be disappointed and think that something like the 515 incident will finally happen.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:49.000
If you are Japanese, you will not want to make your beloved Japan a fine and beautiful planet.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:57.000
If you realize that the result of this dirty vote is so bad for the Japanese parliament,

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:01.000
the Japanese parliament and the Japanese politics,

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:09.000
I don't think it's appropriate to vote for the same cause and the same price as before.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:23.000
Therefore, the Japanese parliament is a deep and grateful sign of the Meiji Emperor.

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:31.000
The election is our right and duty, but it is also a heavy duty.

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:41.000
However, if we make a dirty vote and the result is that there are days of power and power,

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:47.000
we are truly sorry for the great heart of the Meiji Emperor.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:52.000
Please help us to solve the problem of the 515 incident,

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:57.000
which is already shown by the director of the Meiji Emperor,

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:00.000
with a great vote that is not shameful to both sides.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:05.000
I don't doubt that this is the most important job of the modern people.

